<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Partner Programme | Andrew Pritchard</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap');

:root {
  --bg: #071126;
  --bg2: #0a1628;
  --cyan: #00e5ff;
  --cyan-dim: rgba(0,229,255,0.12);
  --cyan-border: rgba(0,229,255,0.22);
  --green: #00ff88;
  --green-dim: rgba(0,255,136,0.1);
  --green-border: rgba(0,255,136,0.25);
  --purple: #7b61ff;
  --white: #f0f4ff;
  --mid: rgba(240,244,255,0.75);
  --dim: rgba(240,244,255,0.4);
}

* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior:smooth; }
body {
  font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
  background:var(--bg); color:var(--white); line-height:1.7;
  overflow-x:hidden;
}
body::before {
  content:''; position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:0; pointer-events:none;
  background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,transparent,transparent 2px,rgba(0,229,255,0.01) 2px,rgba(0,229,255,0.01) 4px);
}
.grid-bg {
  position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:0; pointer-events:none;
  background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(0,229,255,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,229,255,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px);
  background-size:60px 60px;
}
.glow {
  position:fixed; top:-100px; right:-100px;
  width:700px; height:700px; border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,229,255,0.06) 0%,transparent 70%);
  pointer-events:none; z-index:0;
}
.glow2 {
  position:fixed; bottom:-100px; left:-100px;
  width:500px; height:500px; border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(123,97,255,0.06) 0%,transparent 70%);
  pointer-events:none; z-index:0;
}

/* NAV */
nav {
  position:fixed; top:0; width:100%; z-index:100;
  background:rgba(6,14,31,0.95); backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--cyan-border);
  padding:0 48px; height:64px;
  display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
}
.nav-logo { font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; color:var(--cyan); font-size:0.85rem; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-decoration:none; }
.nav-logo span { color:var(--dim); }
.nav-back { font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:0.72rem; color:var(--dim); letter-spacing:0.08em; text-decoration:none; text-transform:uppercase; transition:color 0.2s; }
.nav-back:hover { color:var(--cyan); }

/* HERO */
.hero {
  padding:130px 48px 88px; position:relative; z-index:1;
  max-width:960px; margin:0 auto;
}
.hero-tag {
  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
  background:var(--green-dim); border:1px solid var(--green-border);
  color:var(--green); font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;
  font-size:0.68rem; letter-spacing:0.12em; padding:6px 16px;
  border-radius:20px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:28px;
}
.hero-tag::before { content:'●'; font-size:0.5rem; }
h1 { font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4.5vw,3.6rem); font-weight:800; letter-spacing:-0.03em; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:20px; }
h1 .accent { color:var(--cyan); }
.hero-sub { font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--mid); max-width:580px; margin-bottom:40px; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; }
.hero-ctas { display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.btn {
  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
  font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:0.84rem;
  letter-spacing:0.03em; padding:13px 24px; border-radius:8px;
  text-decoration:none; transition:all 0.2s; border:1px solid; cursor:pointer;
}
.btn-cyan { background:var(--cyan); color:var(--bg); border-color:var(--cyan); }
.btn-cyan:hover { background:rgba(0,229,255,0.85); box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,229,255,0.25); transform:translateY(-1px); }
.btn-outline { background:transparent; color:var(--cyan); border-color:var(--cyan); }
.btn-outline:hover { background:var(--cyan-dim); }
.btn-green { background:var(--green-dim); color:var(--green); border-color:var(--green-border); }
.btn-green:hover { background:rgba(0,255,136,0.18); }

/* TRUST STRIP */
.trust-strip {
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border-top:1px solid var(--cyan-border); border-bottom:1px solid var(--cyan-border);
  padding:32px 48px; position:relative; z-index:1;
}
.trust-inner { max-width:960px; margin:0 auto; display:flex; gap:40px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.trust-item { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--mid); }
.trust-item .ti-num { font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:1.2rem; color:var(--cyan); font-weight:700; }
.trust-divider { width:1px; height:32px; background:var(--cyan-border); flex-shrink:0; }

/* SECTIONS */
section { padding:88px 48px; position:relative; z-index:1; }
.section-inner { max-width:960px; margin:0 auto; }
.sys-tag {
  font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:0.65rem; letter-spacing:0.18em;
  color:var(--cyan); text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:14px;
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
}
.sys-tag::before { content:'//'; color:var(--purple); }
h2 { font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3vw,2.4rem); font-weight:800; letter-spacing:-0.03em; line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:16px; }
.section-sub { color:var(--mid); max-width:580px; margin-bottom:48px; font-weight:300; font-size:0.97rem; }

/* CARDS */
.card {
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.35); border:1px solid var(--cyan-border);
  border-radius:10px; padding:28px; margin-bottom:16px;
  position:relative; overflow:hidden;
}
.card::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:2px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--purple),var(--cyan)); }
.card.green-card::before { background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--green),var(--cyan)); }
.card-label { font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:0.62rem; color:var(--cyan); letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:10px; }
.card.green-card .card-label { color:var(--green); }
.card h3 { font-size:1rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px; }
.card p { font-size:0.88rem; color:var(--mid); margin-bottom:0; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; }

/* WHO IS THIS FOR */
.who-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; margin-top:8px; }
.who-card {
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border:1px solid var(--cyan-border);
  border-radius:10px; padding:24px 20px;
  transition:border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
}
.who-card:hover { border-color:var(--cyan); transform:translateY(-2px); }
.who-icon { font-size:1.6rem; margin-bottom:12px; }
.who-card h4 { font-size:0.92rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px; }
.who-card p { font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--mid); font-weight:300; margin:0; }

/* HOW IT WORKS */
.steps { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:2px; margin-top:8px; }
.step-card {
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border:1px solid var(--cyan-border);
  padding:28px 22px; position:relative;
}
.step-card:first-child { border-radius:10px 0 0 10px; }
.step-card:last-child { border-radius:0 10px 10px 0; }
.step-card::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:2px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--cyan),var(--purple)); }
.step-num { font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:1.8rem; font-weight:700; color:rgba(0,229,255,0.12); margin-bottom:12px; }
.step-card h4 { font-size:0.88rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px; color:var(--white); }
.step-card p { font-size:0.78rem; color:var(--mid); font-weight:300; margin:0; }

/* COMMISSION TABLE */
.commission-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:20px; margin-top:8px; }
.commission-card {
  border-radius:10px; padding:32px 28px; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
}
.commission-card.passive { background:rgba(0,0,0,0.35); border:1px solid var(--cyan-border); }
.commission-card.active { background:rgba(0,255,136,0.05); border:1px solid var(--green-border); }
.commission-card::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:2px; }
.commission-card.passive::before { background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--purple),var(--cyan)); }
.commission-card.active::before { background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--green),var(--cyan)); }
.commission-tier { font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:0.65rem; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px; }
.commission-card.passive .commission-tier { color:var(--cyan); }
.commission-card.active .commission-tier { color:var(--green); }
.commission-rate { font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:3rem; font-weight:700; line-height:1; margin-bottom:4px; }
.commission-card.passive .commission-rate { color:var(--cyan); }
.commission-card.active .commission-rate { color:var(--green); }
.commission-label { font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--dim); margin-bottom:20px; }
.commission-examples { list-style:none; }
.commission-examples li {
  display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
  padding:9px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  font-size:0.82rem; color:var(--mid);
}
.commission-examples li:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.commission-examples li span:last-child { font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-weight:700; color:var(--white); }
.commission-desc { font-size:0.82rem; color:var(--mid); font-weight:300; margin-top:16px; padding-top:16px; border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }

/* PAYMENT TERMS */
.terms-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; margin-top:8px; }
.term-card {
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border:1px solid var(--cyan-border);
  border-radius:10px; padding:22px 20px;
}
.term-icon { font-size:1.4rem; margin-bottom:10px; }
.term-card h4 { font-size:0.88rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px; }
.term-card p { font-size:0.78rem; color:var(--mid); font-weight:300; margin:0; }

/* WHAT THEY GET */
.student-features { list-style:none; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:12px; margin-top:8px; }
.student-features li {
  display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:12px;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border:1px solid var(--cyan-border);
  border-radius:8px; padding:14px 16px;
  font-size:0.86rem; color:var(--mid);
  transition:border-color 0.2s;
}
.student-features li:hover { border-color:var(--cyan); color:var(--white); }
.student-features li::before { content:'◆'; color:var(--cyan); font-size:0.4rem; margin-top:7px; flex-shrink:0; }

/* FORM */
.form-shell {
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.4); border:1px solid var(--cyan-border);
  border-radius:10px; overflow:hidden; margin-top:8px;
}
.form-header {
  background:rgba(0,229,255,0.04); border-bottom:1px solid var(--cyan-border);
  padding:18px 28px;
}
.form-header-title { font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:0.7rem; color:var(--cyan); letter-spacing:0.1em; }
.form-body { padding:32px 28px; }
.field { margin-bottom:18px; }
.field label { display:block; font-size:0.7rem; color:var(--dim); letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; margin-bottom:7px; }
.field input, .field select, .field textarea {
  width:100%; background:rgba(0,229,255,0.04); border:1px solid var(--cyan-border);
  border-radius:6px; color:var(--white); font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
  font-size:0.9rem; padding:11px 14px; outline:none; transition:border-color 0.2s; appearance:none;
}
.field input:focus, .field select:focus, .field textarea:focus { border-color:var(--cyan); background:rgba(0,229,255,0.07); }
.field textarea { resize:vertical; min-height:90px; }
.field select option { background:var(--bg2); color:var(--white); }
.form-row { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px; }
.form-submit { margin-top:8px; }
.radio-group { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; }
.radio-opt { display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:12px; background:rgba(0,229,255,0.03); border:1px solid var(--cyan-border); border-radius:6px; padding:11px 14px; cursor:pointer; transition:background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; }
.radio-opt:hover { background:var(--cyan-dim); border-color:var(--cyan); }
.radio-opt input[type=radio] { accent-color:var(--cyan); width:16px; height:16px; flex-shrink:0; margin-top:3px; }
.radio-opt span { font-size:0.86rem; color:var(--mid); }
.btn-submit { background:var(--cyan); color:var(--bg); border-color:var(--cyan); font-weight:700; font-size:0.88rem; padding:14px 32px; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; border:none; transition:all 0.2s; }
.btn-submit:hover { background:rgba(0,229,255,0.85); box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,229,255,0.25); }
.btn-submit:disabled { opacity:0.6; cursor:not-allowed; }

.success-msg { display:none; text-align:center; padding:48px 28px; }
.success-msg.show { display:block; }
.success-icon { font-size:2.5rem; margin-bottom:16px; }
.success-msg h3 { font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px; }
.success-msg p { color:var(--mid); font-size:0.88rem; }

/* FAQ */
.faq-list { margin-top:8px; }
.faq-item { border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
.faq-q {
  display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
  padding:18px 0; cursor:pointer; font-size:0.92rem; font-weight:600;
  transition:color 0.2s;
}
.faq-q:hover { color:var(--cyan); }
.faq-toggle { font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; color:var(--cyan); font-size:1.2rem; flex-shrink:0; transition:transform 0.2s; }
.faq-a { display:none; padding-bottom:18px; font-size:0.86rem; color:var(--mid); font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; }
.faq-item.open .faq-a { display:block; }
.faq-item.open .faq-toggle { transform:rotate(45deg); }

footer {
  border-top:1px solid var(--cyan-border);
  text-align:center; padding:28px 48px;
  font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; font-size:0.62rem; color:var(--dim);
  position:relative; z-index:1;
}
footer a { color:var(--cyan); text-decoration:none; }

@media(max-width:800px){
  nav { padding:0 20px; }
  .hero, section { padding:64px 20px; }
  .trust-strip { padding:28px 20px; }
  .trust-divider { display:none; }
  .who-grid, .steps, .commission-grid, .terms-grid, .student-features, .form-row { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .step-card:first-child, .step-card:last-child { border-radius:10px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="grid-bg"></div>
<div class="glow"></div>
<div class="glow2"></div>

<nav>
  <a href="index.html" class="nav-logo">ANDREW<span> // PROFESSIONAL ENGLISH</span></a>
  <a href="index.html" class="nav-back">← Main Site</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-tag">Partner & Referral Programme</div>
  <h1>Refer clients.<br>Earn <span class="accent">recurring commission.</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">If you work with high-performing professionals who need to level up their English — executives, founders, engineers, MBA candidates — I'd like to work with you. Simple referral structure, reliable payouts, and a service your clients will thank you for recommending.</p>
  <div class="hero-ctas">
    <a href="#apply" class="btn btn-cyan">Apply to Partner →</a>
    <a href="#commission" class="btn btn-outline">See Commission Rates</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TRUST STRIP -->
<div class="trust-strip">
  <div class="trust-inner">
    <div class="trust-item"><span class="ti-num">15+</span><span>Years teaching advanced professionals</span></div>
    <div class="trust-divider"></div>
    <div class="trust-item"><span class="ti-num">CELTA</span><span>Cambridge certified</span></div>
    <div class="trust-divider"></div>
    <div class="trust-item"><span class="ti-num">B2–C1+</span><span>Advanced learners only</span></div>
    <div class="trust-divider"></div>
    <div class="trust-item"><span class="ti-num">€245</span><span>per month per student</span></div>
    <div class="trust-divider"></div>
    <div class="trust-item"><span class="ti-num">10–15%</span><span>referral commission</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- WHO IS THIS FOR -->
<section>
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="sys-tag">Ideal Partners</div>
    <h2>Who partners with me</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">The best referral partners are professionals who already work with high-performing non-native English speakers — and who want to add genuine value to their client relationships.</p>
    <div class="who-grid">
      <div class="who-card">
        <div class="who-icon">🎯</div>
        <h4>Executive & Career Coaches</h4>
        <p>Your clients want to perform at the highest level. Language precision is often the gap between where they are and where they want to be.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="who-card">
        <div class="who-icon">🎓</div>
        <h4>MBA & Admissions Consultants</h4>
        <p>Candidates preparing for top business schools need authoritative, precise English — in interviews, essays, and on campus.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="who-card">
        <div class="who-icon">🌍</div>
        <h4>Relocation Consultants</h4>
        <p>Professionals moving to English-speaking environments often need rapid professional language development to hit the ground running.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="who-card">
        <div class="who-icon">📊</div>
        <h4>L&D and HR Managers</h4>
        <p>Corporate teams with international talent often have high-potential employees held back by language precision — not ability.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="who-card">
        <div class="who-icon">🏢</div>
        <h4>Language Schools</h4>
        <p>Schools that don't offer advanced professional English coaching, or that have overflow students beyond their capacity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="who-card">
        <div class="who-icon">💼</div>
        <h4>Outplacement Consultants</h4>
        <p>Professionals in transition who need to present with authority in interviews and new roles — fast.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section style="background:var(--bg2);border-top:1px solid var(--cyan-border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--cyan-border);">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="sys-tag">Process</div>
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Simple by design. No complicated tracking systems or approval processes.</p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <h4>You apply</h4>
        <p>Fill in the short form below. I'll review and get back to you within 48 hours to discuss the partnership.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <h4>You refer</h4>
        <p>Share your unique referral link or introduce a client directly. They book a discovery call via my site.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <h4>They enrol</h4>
        <p>If the client signs up to the monthly or full programme, your commission is triggered automatically.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <h4>You get paid</h4>
        <p>Commission paid monthly via bank transfer or PayPal. Full transparency — you'll receive a statement each month.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- COMMISSION -->
<section id="commission">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="sys-tag">Commission Structure</div>
    <h2>What you earn</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Two tiers based on how actively you refer. Both are paid for the first 3 months of a student's monthly subscription, or as a one-off on the full programme.</p>
    <div class="commission-grid">
      <div class="commission-card passive">
        <div class="commission-tier">// Tier 1 — Passive Referral</div>
        <div class="commission-rate">10%</div>
        <div class="commission-label">Link share or casual introduction</div>
        <ul class="commission-examples">
          <li><span>Monthly plan (per month × 3)</span><span>€24.50/mo</span></li>
          <li><span>Full programme (one-off)</span><span>€245</span></li>
          <li><span>3 students on monthly</span><span>€220.50</span></li>
          <li><span>3 students on full</span><span>€735</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="commission-desc">For partners who share a link or make a casual mention. No expectation of active selling.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="commission-card active">
        <div class="commission-tier">// Tier 2 — Active Referral</div>
        <div class="commission-rate">15%</div>
        <div class="commission-label">Qualified introduction or active pitch</div>
        <ul class="commission-examples">
          <li><span>Monthly plan (per month × 3)</span><span>€36.75/mo</span></li>
          <li><span>Full programme (one-off)</span><span>€367.50</span></li>
          <li><span>3 students on monthly</span><span>€330.75</span></li>
          <li><span>3 students on full</span><span>€1,102.50</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="commission-desc">For partners who actively qualify, brief, and introduce clients — ensuring they arrive informed and motivated.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PAYMENT TERMS -->
<section style="padding-top:0;">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="sys-tag">Payment Terms</div>
    <h2>Clear and simple</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">No surprises. Here's exactly how and when you get paid.</p>
    <div class="terms-grid">
      <div class="term-card">
        <div class="term-icon">📅</div>
